      "author": "yoriGo77",
      "description": "## Highlights\r\n- Full dark-mode adaptation across the panel, columns, cards, context menus and inputs.\r\n- Dedicated bright palette for the highlight menu in dark mode (`#ffe28b` / `#8edf91` / `#82d0f6` / `#f49a82` / `#d6b2ed` / `#f7f5f1`).\r\n- Highlighted cards in dark mode now render as a colored outline with an 18% same-color background fill — clearer than flat pale fills.\r\n- The view automatically refreshes when Obsidian's theme is switched (no manual reload needed).\r\n\r\n## Fixes\r\n- Drag ghost element no longer leaks if the view is closed mid-drag.\r\n- `activateView()` now falls back gracefully when the right side dock is unavailable.\r\n- User-customized colors are preserved across themes; only \"default\" colors auto-adapt.\r\n\r\n## Compatibility\r\n- Desktop only. `minAppVersion: 0.15.0` (see `manifest.json`).\r\n- Existing data is unchanged — saved hex colors are mapped at render time.",
