      "author": "yoriGo77",
      "description": "## v1.0.5\r\n### ✨ Highlights\r\n- Improved board-column drag-and-drop behavior and insertion guidance.\r\n- Added in-plugin language setting (Chinese / English), defaulting to English.\r\n- Localized TASK/WEEK/YEAR titles and archive section headings by language.\r\n- Updated DONE behavior: newly completed tasks now appear first (keeps latest 30).\r\n### ✅ UX Improvements\r\n- WEEK view now switches week by left/right arrows around date range.\r\n- WEEK/YEAR headers updated to language-aware formats.\r\n- YEAR topbar now shows year only.\r\n- Refined task edit input visuals and alignment consistency.\r\n- Removed unwanted arrow button white background/border in WEEK topbar.\r\n### 🛠 Fixes\r\n- Fixed multi-column drag edge cases (2/3-column layouts).\r\n- Fixed no-op drag indicator showing at original position.\r\n- Fixed insertion indicator behavior on row starts/ends and boundary zones.\r\n- Ensured archive note block titles follow current language rules.\r\n### 🧪 Validation\r\n- Local test suite passed: `17/17`.",
